<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 13:18:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>MHRA 警告使用肉毒杆菌毒素后存在肉毒杆菌中毒风险</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/mhra-warns-of-botulism-risk-after-botulinum-toxin-use</link><description>MHRA 的最新警报警告了未经许可和假冒肉毒毒素产品的危险。凯夫说：“我们还强烈敦促公众避免使用未经许可的产品，只向合格的从业人员寻求治疗。” &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/mhra-warns-of-botulism-risk-after-botulinum-toxin-use.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 13:18:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/mhra-warns-of-botulism-risk-after-botulinum-toxin-use</guid></item><item><title>埃利亚斯·索恩的奇怪案例，人工智能聊天机器人痴迷的想象中的人</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-strange-case-of-elias-thorne-the-imaginary-man-ai-chatbots-are-obsessed-with</link><description>无论是哪家公司，人工智能聊天机器人都对同一个名叫埃利亚斯·索恩的人赞不绝口。他一定很迷人。他确实是，至少在纸面上是这样。根据人工智能的不同，他是一名灯塔看守人、一名钟表匠、一名图书管理员、一名探险家，以及无数故事中的明星。他出现在书籍、音乐列表、YouTube 视频甚至健康指南中。你可能会认为他是地球上最有影响力的人之一。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-strange-case-of-elias-thorne-the-imaginary-man-ai-chatbots-are-obsessed-with.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 13:03:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-strange-case-of-elias-thorne-the-imaginary-man-ai-chatbots-are-obsessed-with</guid></item><item><title>隆重推出 Gemini 3.6 Flash、3.5 Flash-Lite 和 3.5 Flash Cyber</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/introducing-gemini-3-6-flash-3-5-flash-lite-and-3-5-flash-cyber</link><description>我们推出了新的 Gemini 型号，包括 Gemini 3.6 Flash、3.5 Flash-Lite 和 3.5 Flash Cyber​​。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/introducing-gemini-3-6-flash-3-5-flash-lite-and-3-5-flash-cyber.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 12:48:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/introducing-gemini-3-6-flash-3-5-flash-lite-and-3-5-flash-cyber</guid></item><item><title>微型忆阻器芯片将大脑建模时间缩短至 10 毫秒以下</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/tiny-memristor-chip-cuts-brain-modeling-time-to-under-10-milliseconds</link><description>一个研究小组开发出了世界上第一个可以与人脑运行速度相匹配的芯片。这项研究的标题是“基于相变忆阻器的亚 10 毫秒神经动力系统” &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/tiny-memristor-chip-cuts-brain-modeling-time-to-under-10-milliseconds2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 12:33:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/tiny-memristor-chip-cuts-brain-modeling-time-to-under-10-milliseconds</guid></item><item><title>加州大学洛杉矶分校的科学家重新编程干细胞以产生可再生的抗癌 T 细胞</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/ucla-scientists-reprogram-stem-cells-to-create-renewable-cancerfighting-t-cells</link><description>临床试验表明，结合基因工程T细胞和干细胞可以在人体中产生抗癌免疫细胞。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ucla-scientists-reprogram-stem-cells-to-create-renewable-cancerfighting-t-cells.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 12:18:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/ucla-scientists-reprogram-stem-cells-to-create-renewable-cancerfighting-t-cells</guid></item><item><title>加州大学洛杉矶分校的科学家发现僵尸免疫细胞是脂肪肝疾病、炎症和衰老的驱动因素</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/ucla-scientists-identify-zombie-immune-cells-as-a-driver-of-fatty-liver-disease-inflammation-and-aging</link><description>研究发现，过量的饮食胆固醇，而不仅仅是衰老，可以将这些免疫细胞推入永久性发炎状态。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ucla-scientists-identify-zombie-immune-cells-as-a-driver-of-fatty-liver-disease-inflammation-and-aging.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 12:03:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/ucla-scientists-identify-zombie-immune-cells-as-a-driver-of-fatty-liver-disease-inflammation-and-aging</guid></item><item><title>术后子宫超声：相关影像的长期发现</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/us-of-the-postprocedure-uterus-longterm-findings-with-correlative-imaging</link><description>了解剖腹产、宫内节育器放置、子宫内膜消融和肌瘤栓塞等常见手术后的预期子宫外观对于内部治疗至关重要。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/us-of-the-postprocedure-uterus-longterm-findings-with-correlative-imaging2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 11:48:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/us-of-the-postprocedure-uterus-longterm-findings-with-correlative-imaging</guid></item><item><title>阿帕替尼通过 Drp1 介导的内皮线粒体分裂引起高血压</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/apatinib-causes-hypertension-via-drp1mediated-endothelial-mitochondrial-fission</link><description>背景：阿帕替尼是一种酪氨酸激酶抑制剂，用于癌症靶向治疗，但其心血管毒性，特别是高血压，限制了其临床应用。我们观察到阿帕替尼治疗后内皮细胞中出现显着的线粒体碎片。本研究旨在探讨Drp1（动力相关蛋白1）介导的内皮线粒体分裂在阿帕替尼诱导的高血压中的作用。方法：建立阿帕替尼靶向胃癌裸鼠模型。阿帕替尼也被用于体外人脐静脉内皮细胞。检查内皮细胞的线粒体形态变化。使用各种实验方法验证了 Drp1 在此过程中的作用。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/apatinib-causes-hypertension-via-drp1mediated-endothelial-mitochondrial-fission2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 11:33:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/apatinib-causes-hypertension-via-drp1mediated-endothelial-mitochondrial-fission</guid></item><item><title>使用 T 细胞受体可变基因探针进行 T 细胞克隆型分析的空间原位杂交方法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/a-spatial-in-situ-hybridization-approach-to-t-cell-clonotype-analysis-using-t-cell-receptor-variable-gene-probes</link><description>莱等人。开发了一个空间&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-spatial-in-situ-hybridization-approach-to-t-cell-clonotype-analysis-using-t-cell-receptor-variable-gene-probes2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 11:18:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/a-spatial-in-situ-hybridization-approach-to-t-cell-clonotype-analysis-using-t-cell-receptor-variable-gene-probes</guid></item><item><title>JCI：斯特拉斯堡大学，Inserm，转化医学和肝病研究所，UMR_S1110，斯特拉斯堡，法国</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/jci-university-of-strasbourg-inserm-institute-for-translational-medicine-and-liver-disease-umr_s1110-strasbourg-france</link><description>2&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/jci2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 11:03:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/jci-university-of-strasbourg-inserm-institute-for-translational-medicine-and-liver-disease-umr_s1110-strasbourg-france</guid></item></channel></rss>